<TEXT>Year 1072 (MLXXII) was a leap year starting on Sunday (link will display the full calendar) of the Julian calendar.
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>35934_3</DOCNO>
<TEXT><onlyinclude>
</TEXT>
