<DOCNO>36189_2</DOCNO>
<TEXT>Year 1221 (MCCXXI) was a common year starting on Friday (link will display the full calendar) of the Julian calendar. 
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>36189_3</DOCNO>
<TEXT><onlyinclude>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>36189_4</DOCNO>
<TEXT>(The Jews were falsely accused of a ritual murder. A crowd stormed the synagogue where the Jews had gathered. As usual the threat was baptism or death. The Jewish quarter including the synagogue was razed, many Jews were tortured and killed. Among the martyrs were Shem Tov ha-Levi, and Rabbi and Mrs. Shmuel Kalonymos, Hy'd.) 
</TEXT>
</DOC>
