<DOC>
<DOCNO>36190_2</DOCNO>
<TEXT>Year 1459 (MCDLIX) was a common year starting on Monday (link will display the full calendar) of the Julian calendar.
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>36190_3</DOCNO>
<TEXT><onlyinclude>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
