<DOCNO>36398_1</DOCNO>
<TEXT>2020s

</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>36398_2</DOCNO>
<TEXT>The 2020s (pronounced as "twenty-twenties" or "two-thousand (and) twenties") is a decade of the Gregorian calendar. It will begin on January 1, 2020 and will end on December 31, 2029.
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>36399_1</DOCNO>
<TEXT>721

